<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink59-kilavi">
      <p type="edition">talaimakaṟkup puṟattoḻukkam uḷatāyiṟṟu eṉpatu kēṭṭa tōḻi avaṉai viṉāyatu.
      </p>
      <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="Aink59">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>kēṭṭiciṉ vāḻiyō makiḻna vāṟṟuṟa</l>
<l>maiya  ṉeñciṟ kevvan tīra</l>
<l>niṉakkumarun tākiya yāṉiṉi</l>
<l>yivaṭkumarun taṉmai nōme ṉeñcē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">




<l>   Please listen, o delightful man, and may you live long! </l> 
<l> I was [once] a medicine </l> 
<l> to end the sorrow of your infatuated heart</l> 
<l> so that it would begin to be soothed. </l> 
<p/>
<l> I am no medicine to her now, </l> 
<l> and my heart aches. </l> 



</lg>
    </div>
